        "value": "i1"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The standard deviation of <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"y\"><math alttext=\"y\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mi>y</mi></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> does not vary as <span class=\"math_expression\"><span aria-label=\"x\"><math alttext=\"x\" display=\"inline\" overflow=\"scroll\"><mstyle><mrow><mstyle><mrow><mi>x</mi></mrow></mstyle></mrow></mstyle></math></span></span> varies.</p>",
        "value": "i2"
      },
      {
        "label": "<p class=\"choice_paragraph\">The correlation is not equal to zero.</p>",
